Author: situationtypedill
Text: Update: I did an hour on the elliptical, lifted some weights, and did another 20 minutes on the elliptical because I felt like it wasn’t enough. I still feel like I didn’t burn enough off today but my feet were going numb so I figured it was best to stop. I’ll probably do the same workout tomorrow morning

Author: kangaroojackcoffee
Text: Be proud of yourself for modeling healthy eating habits in front of your sweet niece and letting her know that it’s okay to eat Mac and Cheese!
